Class BarcodeGraphicTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.gms.vision.Tracker<com.google.android.gms.vision.barcode.Barcode>
      • vl.team07.com.virtuallibrary.Scanner.BarcodeGraphicTracker

  • class BarcodeGraphicTracker
extends com.google.android.gms.vision.Tracker<com.google.android.gms.vision.barcode.Barcode>
    Generic tracker which is used for tracking or reading a barcode (and can really be used for any type of item). This is used to receive newly detected items, add a graphical representation to an overlay, update the graphics as the item changes, and remove the graphics when the item goes away.
